---
import Section from "./Section.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import mothman from "../assets/mothman.jpg";
---

<Section title="Cryptid of the Month">
  <div class="bg-white/80 p-6 rounded-xs shadow-md">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 bg-white rounded-xs drop-shadow-md p-4">
        <Image 
          src={mothman} 
          alt="Mothman" 
          width={400} 
          height={300} 
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2 font-mono uppercase">Mothman</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">First spotted in Point Pleasant, West Virginia in 1966, Mothman is described as a large, winged humanoid with glowing red eyes. Standing 7 feet tall with a wingspan of 10-15 feet, this mysterious creature has been linked to disasters and strange phenomena.</p>
        <div class="mt-4">
          <a href="/files" class="text-blue-900 font-mono hover:underline">View all cryptid files â†’</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
